data.description: This Ranch style 2 story home has 1906 sqft of room to offer for those family gatherings. This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home has granite counter tops, S/S appliances and an apron sink to give you that ranch style feel. With the wrap around porch you can gaze off into the open pasture or enjoy the beautiful large oak trees. You can even have those farm fresh eggs with the chicken coop in the backyard. The 1.71 acres will give you the country feel with all the city amenities. Master bedroom and 1 guest bedroom or office on main level all other rooms upstairs.
